32:06.424 --> 32:11.797 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
LOURDES GARCIA-NAVARRO: You're
welcome.

32:11.830 --> 32:18.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: This is the day
that the tax
man cometh, or, more accurately,
the day when

32:18.537 --> 32:22.240 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
