of taxpayers.

32:49.868 --> 32:51.703 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
John Koskinen joins me now.

32:51.736 --> 32:53.305 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Mr. Koskinen, thank you for
being with us.

32:53.338 --> 32:55.106 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN KOSKINEN, IRS Commissioner:
Delighted
to be here.

32:55.140 --> 32:58.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: What is it going
to take to
restore the confidence of the
American people

32:58.577 --> 33:00.345 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
in the IRS?

33:00.378 --> 33:02.747 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KOSKINEN: Well, I think
what we have
to do is first demonstrate to
them that it's

33:02.781 --> 33:07.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a fair system, that, if you hear
from us,
it's because of something in
your return,

33:07.319 --> 33:10.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
