can hire
people, they will be able to
answer the phone.

36:48.106 --> 36:51.543 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you don't give us money, we
can't hire
the people during filling
season, and it will

36:51.576 --> 36:53.378 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
