36:53.411 --> 36:56.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Would it be
easier if -- we
know some of the Republican
candidates for

36:56.514 --> 37:00.985 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
