anywhere in the world is getting
a lot more

38:36.414 --> 38:38.216 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
difficult.

38:38.249 --> 38:42.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Do you find that
it's now much
easier to go after these
individuals because

38:42.487 --> 38:45.823 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
