does this -- how
much difference does this make?

38:45.857 --> 38:49.060 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KOSKINEN: Well, I think
this reporting
will help. We're working with a
number of

38:49.093 --> 38:54.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
tax administrations around the
world to collect
this particular data and
cooperate on following

38:54.165 --> 38:55.934 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
through with it.

38:55.967 --> 38:59.404 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I think what's happening for
compliance
