think, wealthy

38:59.437 --> 39:03.808 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
investors and taxpayers around
the world are
discovering that there is a
growing global

39:03.841 --> 39:08.680 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
