Revenue Service, on Tax Day,
thank you for

39:15.253 --> 39:16.120 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
joining us.

39:16.154 --> 39:22.126 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN KOSKINEN: Thanks for
